== Extracted Lists

 The list environments below are extracted from arXiv LaTeX source and wrapped for pdfLaTeX validation.

  + i) Physical states that enter the couplings.
  + ii) Allowed couplings.
  + iii) Numerical values of the Yukawa couplings and dependence of these values on the physical parameters that define the string vacuum (e.g. the size of the compactified space).
  + iv) Number of different Yukawa couplings and phenomenological viability of the scheme ($i . e . $ fitting of the observed pattern of fermion masses and mixing angles by the theoretical Yukawa couplings).

